It was love at first sight for Sreya and Vishal. However, Sreya is tormented by demons from her past, and she turns down Vishal, the college heartthrob. Will their intense chemistry triumph over her dark past?  Kavya falls desperately in love with Aadhi. Aadhi loves Kavya too, but only on his own terms. Things then start to go incredibly wrong. Will their love succeed?  Anand and Priya are quiz partners, project partners and great friends. But is there more than what meets the eye? Are they secretly in love with each other?  Join the fun-loving group of close-knit friends studying in an engineering college, having the time of their life while following their passions and dreams!